Grease and flour three 7 x 3 inch pans. Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Measure flour, sugar, baking soda, salt, and spices into a large bowl. Stir to blend. Add pumpkin, water, vegetable oil, eggs, and nuts. Beat until well combined. Pour batter into prepared pans. Bake for approximately 1 hour.